These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, van
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, disco
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, february
2 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret
1. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the fan of disco##8
2. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
3. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Transport      | van     | bike      |
| Music-Genre          | disco | punk    |
| Birthday         | february   | september |
| Pet   | hamster  | ferret      |

