.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, july
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, ice-hockey
There 2 different types of food: grapes, grapefruit
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
2. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
4. the person eating grapes is not the cape-cod house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Birthday    | october        | july    |
| House       | gothic-revival         | cape-cod |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | water-polo   |
| Food   | grapes               | grapefruit  |

