.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, cucumber
City: miami, liverpool
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
2 different games are played: go, monopoly
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
3. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Food   | grapefruit       | cucumber |
| City   | miami       | liverpool    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Game           | go        | monopoly   |

