2. the person who growszinnia is not to the left of the cape-cod house##8
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Flower         | aconite | zinnia  |
| Sport           | volleyball  | climbing |
| Pet   | chinchilla | dog   |
| House     | cape-cod   | townhouse |

