.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, card-games
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, december
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, electronic
1. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Hobby          | card-games         | traveling    |
| Sport           | badminton | biathlon   |
| Birthday   | january   | december    |
| Music-Genre     | r&b         | electronic |

 